query:
SELECT
    b.name,
    b.address,
    b.state,
    b.stars,
    b.review_count,
    GROUP_CONCAT(c.category, ', ') AS all_categories
FROM business b
LEFT JOIN category c ON b.id = c.business_id
GROUP BY b.id
LIMIT 10000
